  <div id="tplPage" class="wspUi"><div id="tplTitle"><div id="tplTitleLogo"><img src="../res/logoOpale3.png" alt width="48" height="48"></div><span id="tplTitleMain">Opale</span><span id="tplTitlesub">&quot;Academic&quot; pedagogical content creation</span></div><div id="tplTabs"><div id="tplTabCo"><div id="tplTabCoScroll"><div class="infoblock"><h1 class="infoblock_ti">Who is <span class="txt_vName_el ">Opale</span> for?</h1><div class="infoblock_co"><div class="text "><ul class="txt_il "><li class="txt_ili "><p class="txt_p ">For trainers and teachers wishing to create rich training modules for on-site training, distance or blended learning.</p></li><li class="txt_ili "><p class="txt_p ">For organizations, training centers and schools, seeking a tool to produce and publish pedagogical content.</p></li></ul></div></div></div><div class="infoblock"><h1 class="infoblock_ti">Why use <span class="txt_vName_el ">Opale</span>?</h1><div class="infoblock_co"><div class="text "><p class="txt_p "><strong class="txt_emphasis_is ">Pour...</strong></p><ul class="txt_il "><li class="txt_ili "><p class="txt_p ">Produce accessible online training modules (html) and print resources;</p></li><li class="txt_ili "><p class="txt_p ">Create a slideshow;</p></li><li class="txt_ili "><p class="txt_p ">Create SCORM 1.2 or SCORM 2004 compliant training content and publish them via a Learning Management System (LMS);</p></li><li class="txt_ili "><p class="txt_p ">Facilitate content updates thanks to single sourcing mechanisms: a single source of content, multiple output media;</p></li><li class="txt_ili "><p class="txt_p ">Improve your content by adding multimedia resources (videos, animations, sounds, images, diagrams, mathematical formulae,...);</p></li><li class="txt_ili "><p class="txt_p ">Improve your content by adding quizzes automatically managed by <span class="txt_vName_el ">Opale</span> (Single Choice Questions, Multiple Choice Questions, Drag &amp; drop, Fill-in the gaps,...);</p></li><li class="txt_ili "><p class="txt_p ">Optimize information management and updates by creating elements re-usable in different scenarios and output media (single source of content, multiple output media);</p></li><li class="txt_ili "><p class="txt_p ">Generate several  versions of the same module (<cite class="txt_alt_is ">standard version</cite> and <cite class="txt_alt_is ">short version</cite>) thanks to a filter mechanism;</p></li><li class="txt_ili "><p class="txt_p ">Organize the work and reviews of a team.</p></li></ul><p class="txt_p "><strong class="txt_emphasis_is ">And also to...</strong></p><ul class="txt_il "><li class="txt_ili "><p class="txt_p ">Bring a homogenous graphic identity to all your training documents;</p></li><li class="txt_ili "><p class="txt_p ">Ensure content durability by saving it in an XML format that does not depend on the publishing tool.</p></li></ul></div></div></div><div class="infoblock"><h1 class="infoblock_ti">How to use <span class="txt_vName_el ">Opale</span>?</h1><div class="infoblock_co"><div class="text "><p class="txt_p ">The <code class="txt_textTab_tl ">Quick help</code> tab of this area provides some hints of <span class="txt_vName_el ">Opale</span> structure and items.</p><p class="txt_p ">For further information, please refer to the <a class="txt_url_ul " target="_blank" href="http://scenari-platform.org/projects/opale/fr/pres/co/documentation.html" title="http://scenari-platform.org/projects/opale/fr/pres/co/documentation.html"><span>user guider (fr)</span></a> available from the scenari-platform website.</p></div></div></div><div class="infoblock"><h1 class="infoblock_ti">Personalize your <span class="txt_vName_el ">Opale</span></h1><div class="infoblock_co"><div class="text "><p class="txt_p ">Depending on your needs:</p><ul class="txt_sl "><li class="txt_m "><span>Download one of the freely available skins provided by the community in  <a class="txt_url_ul " target="_blank" href="http://scenari-platform.org/addons/" title="http://scenari-platform.org/addons/"><span>Addons</span></a> (available under &quot;Habillage graphique&quot;) and new publications such as direct PDF output, SCENARIreader output,...);</span></li><li class="txt_m "><span>Create your own skin with SCENARIstyler, available for download on the <a class="txt_url_ul " target="_blank" href="http://scenari-platform.org/projects/scenari/fr/download/co/" title="http://scenari-platform.org/projects/scenari/fr/download/co/"><span>scenari-platform</span></a> website.</span></li></ul></div></div></div><div class="advice block"><h1 class="advice_ti block_ti"><span class="block_ti_co"><span class="blockTitle">OpenDocument publishing</span></span></h1><div class="advice_co block_co"><div class="text "><p class="txt_p ">If a problem occurs when publishing paper documents or web documents with OpenDocument tables or graphs, check that you installed precisely the recommended version of  LibreOffice (4.2.6), and you might also need to configure it's path in some case, with the menu: <code class="txt_menuPath_tl ">Application / Preferences / General / External tools</code>.</p></div></div></div><div class="advice block"><h1 class="advice_ti block_ti"><span class="block_ti_co"><span class="blockTitle">LaTeX</span></span></h1><div class="advice_co block_co"><div class="text "><p class="txt_p ">If you wish to use LaTeX mathematical formulae, you need to install a LaTeX engine.</p><p class="txt_p ">You will find further information on the page: <a class="txt_url_ul " target="_blank" href="http://scenari-platform.org/projects/opale/doc/permalink/latex?product=opale&amp;ver=3.4" title="http://scenari-platform.org/projects/opale/doc/permalink/latex?product=opale&amp;ver=3.4"><span>aide &agrave; l'installation LaTeX (fr)</span></a>.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div id="tplTabBar"><span class=" tabSel_yes"><span>Presentation</span></span><a href="structure.html" target="_self" class=" tabSel_no"><span>Quick help</span></a><a href="nvtes.html" target="_self" class=" tabSel_no"><span>New features</span></a><a href="Opale_Advanced.html" target="_self" class=" tabSel_no"><span>About...</span></a></div></div></div>
